reviews.review_text: Pretty Vanilla This is a typical 80’s show. If you are not a fan of that era look for another show to listen to. Good song selection, no major mistakes and it seems Jerry remembered the words better than Bobby! I personally enjoyed the show, as this was the era that I saw most of my shows. Nice to hear Brent singing too!
clever love the "no count" intro to BIODTL
